        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The view "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "CrisNationalGridWest.uvw_CRIS_UploadPreloadDataCount",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to aggregate and present row counts from multiple tables within the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "CrisNationalGridWest",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema. Each table represents a different type of data preload related to billing and account management. The view consolidates these counts by "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "BillingPeriod",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", providing a unified perspective on the volume of data across different preload tables. This is achieved using a series of "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "UNION ALL",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " operations, which combine the results of individual "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "SELECT",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " statements, each counting rows grouped by "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "BillingPeriod",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
